<li id="cite_note-pmid1441462-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid1441462_18-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFGartrell_N.2C_Milliken_N.2C_Goodson_W.2C_Thiemann_S.2C_Lo_B1992">Gartrell N, Milliken N, Goodson W, Thiemann S, Lo B (1992). "Physician-patient sexual contact. Prevalence and problems". <i>West J Med</i> <b>157</b> (2): 139–43. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1441462" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1441462">PMID 1441462</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Physician-patient+sexual+contact.+Prevalence+and+problems&amp;rft.jtitle=West+J+Med&amp;rft.aulast=Gartrell+N%2C+Milliken+N%2C+Goodson+W%2C+Thiemann+S%2C+Lo+B&amp;rft.au=Gartrell+N%2C+Milliken+N%2C+Goodson+W%2C+Thiemann+S%2C+Lo+B&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.volume=157&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=139%E2%80%9343&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/1441462&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Medical_ethics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> JM Appel. May Physicians Date Their Patients’ Relatives? Rethinking Sexual Misconduct &amp; Disclosure After Long v. Ostroff, Medicine &amp; Health, Rhode Island, May 2004</li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://medethics.org.il/articles/FIC/15.pdf" class="external text" title="http://medethics.org.il/articles/FIC/15.pdf" rel="nofollow">New Horizons on the Subject of Medical Ethics</a>published by the <a href="/wiki/Schlesinger_institute" title="Schlesinger institute">Schlesinger institute</a></li>
